Interface Dimension

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DimensionImpl

    public interface Dimension
    A representation of the model object 'Dimension'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Width
    • Height

    See Also:
    VisualInterfacePackage.getDimension()
